{"tid":637000,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[BLINK] BLACKPINK討論區 (16) 只有五首歌的日巡","createTime":"2018-04-21T12:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T12:07:38.000Z","uid":8280,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f8114c8a9a23880002a9cbfa00ed4c8edd1a66","tid":637000,"uid":8280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Da99knfU8AAe0eD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDa99knfU8AAe0eD.jpg&h=1d17f854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">BLACKPINK</span></strong>（韓語：블랙핑크）是YG娛樂於2016年推出的韓國女子音樂組合，由JISOO、JENNIE、ROS&Eacute;與LISA四名成員組成。2016年8月8日以數碼專輯《SQUARE ONE》正式出道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbS3w0-VwAAOttP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbS3w0-VwAAOttP.jpg&h=98b9fdbe&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://2sao.vietnamnetjsc.vn/images/2018/01/04/10/13/black-pink-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2sao.vietnamnetjsc.vn%2Fimages%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F10%2F13%2Fblack-pink-2.jpg&h=e0011982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYG娛樂表示BLACK PINK帶有稍微否定粉紅色是最美的顏色的涵義，具有「漂亮並不代表全部」的反轉意義，也表示成員們不僅具備外貌、同時也兼具實力。<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK 將於 7 月 20 日搶先在武道館舉行 showcase《BLACKPINK PREMIUM DEBUT SHOWCASE》，並於 8 月 30 日正式發行出道專輯。<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK 宣告將於7月舉辦首次日本巡迴演出&ldquo;BLACKPINK ARENA TOUR 2018&rdquo;。 7月24日得大阪公演為開始，在福岡、千葉等日本三大城市共舉辦六場演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CpVnIctUEAEN8Jj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCpVnIctUEAEN8Jj.jpg&h=99f96d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一張數碼專輯《SQUARE ONE》<br />\n發行日期：2016年8月8日<br />\n主打曲:<br />\n1.휘파람（WHISTLE）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dISNgvVpWlo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdISNgvVpWlo&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d4258e42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dISNgvVpWlo</a><br />\n2.붐바야（BOOMBAYAH）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bwmSjveL3Lc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbwmSjveL3Lc&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=52460406\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bwmSjveL3Lc</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CxQArD7WgAACk_H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCxQArD7WgAACk_H.jpg&h=fcd89d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二張數碼專輯《SQUARE TWO》<br />\n發行日期：2016年11月1日<br />\n主打曲<br />\n1.불장난（PLAYING WITH FIRE）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pdj4iJD08s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9pdj4iJD08s&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=650c58b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pdj4iJD08s</a><br />\n2.STAY<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzVR_fymZw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFzVR_fymZw4&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=525dcf63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzVR_fymZw4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DC6n1aOU0AA5-EN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDC6n1aOU0AA5-EN.jpg&h=061b0819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一隻數碼單曲《마지막처럼》(AS IF IT<code>S YOUR LAST)\n發行日期：2017年06月22日\n主打曲\n1. 마지막처럼 (AS IF IT</code>S YOUR LAST)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Amq-qlqbjYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAmq-qlqbjYA&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=edca8646\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Amq-qlqbjYA</a><br />\n<br />\nJAPAN DEBUT MINI ALBUM『BLACKPINK』<br 